    <item>
      <title>Organizer Handbook</title>
      <link>https://example.com/handbook/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://example.com/handbook/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;welcome--how-to-use-this&#34;&gt;Welcome &amp;amp; how to use this&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Thank you for helping run Your Community. Organizing is a team effort, and you are never expected to do it alone. This handbook is the &lt;em&gt;why&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;what&lt;/em&gt;, the principles and expectations. The &lt;a href=&#34;https://example.com/runbooks/&#34;&gt;Runbooks&lt;/a&gt; are the &lt;em&gt;how&lt;/em&gt;, tick-box checklists you follow the week of an event.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;g-callout&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-circle-info&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;g-callout__body&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;g-callout__title&#34;&gt;Our north star&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Every decision comes back to one question: &lt;em&gt;will this help someone who has never been to a meetup feel welcome here?&lt;/em&gt; If yes, we&amp;rsquo;re on the right track.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
