    <item>
      <title>About us</title>
      <link>https://example.com/about/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://example.com/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Write two or three warm paragraphs about your community: who it&amp;rsquo;s for, what a gathering looks like, and that newcomers are always welcome.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;land-acknowledgement&#34;&gt;Land acknowledgement&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Add your community&amp;rsquo;s land acknowledgement or welcome statement here, or remove this section.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;common-questions&#34;&gt;Common questions&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;g-faq&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;details class=&#34;g-faq__item&#34; open&gt;&#xA;  &lt;summary class=&#34;g-faq__q&#34;&gt;Do I need experience to join?&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;g-faq__a g-prose&#34;&gt;No. Newcomers are exactly who this is for, come as you are.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details class=&#34;g-faq__item&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;summary class=&#34;g-faq__q&#34;&gt;Is it free?&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;g-faq__a g-prose&#34;&gt;Yes. Events are free to attend.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details class=&#34;g-faq__item&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;summary class=&#34;g-faq__q&#34;&gt;How do I find the room?&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;g-faq__a g-prose&#34;&gt;Check the event page for arrival notes (buzz codes, door instructions). If in doubt, ask an organizer when you arrive.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;script type=&#34;application/ld+json&#34;&gt;{&#34;@context&#34;:&#34;https://schema.org&#34;,&#34;@type&#34;:&#34;FAQPage&#34;,&#34;mainEntity&#34;:[{&#34;@type&#34;:&#34;Question&#34;,&#34;acceptedAnswer&#34;:{&#34;@type&#34;:&#34;Answer&#34;,&#34;text&#34;:&#34;No. Newcomers are exactly who this is for, come as you are.&#34;},&#34;name&#34;:&#34;Do I need experience to join?&#34;},{&#34;@type&#34;:&#34;Question&#34;,&#34;acceptedAnswer&#34;:{&#34;@type&#34;:&#34;Answer&#34;,&#34;text&#34;:&#34;Yes. Events are free to attend.&#34;},&#34;name&#34;:&#34;Is it free?&#34;},{&#34;@type&#34;:&#34;Question&#34;,&#34;acceptedAnswer&#34;:{&#34;@type&#34;:&#34;Answer&#34;,&#34;text&#34;:&#34;Check the event page for arrival notes (buzz codes, door instructions). If in doubt, ask an organizer when you arrive.&#34;},&#34;name&#34;:&#34;How do I find the room?&#34;}]}&lt;/script&gt;</description>
    </item>
