    <item>
      <title>Code of Conduct</title>
      <link>https://example.com/code-of-conduct/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://example.com/code-of-conduct/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-short-version&#34;&gt;The short version&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Be kind. Be respectful. Assume good faith. Your Community is a community of people with a wide range of backgrounds and experience, and we&amp;rsquo;re here to enjoy this together. Harassment and exclusionary behaviour are never acceptable.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;expected-behaviour&#34;&gt;Expected behaviour&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Be welcoming, friendly and patient, especially with newcomers.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Be considerate in your speech and actions, and respectful of differing viewpoints.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Assume the person you&amp;rsquo;re talking to knows things you don&amp;rsquo;t, and vice versa.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Give others space and time to speak; make room for quieter voices.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;unacceptable-behaviour&#34;&gt;Unacceptable behaviour&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Harassment, intimidation, or discrimination in any form.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Offensive comments related to gender, gender identity, sexual orientation, disability, physical appearance, race, ethnicity, religion or experience level.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Unwelcome sexual attention, or deliberate intimidation, stalking or following.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Sustained disruption of sessions or other events.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Photographing or recording someone without their consent.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;g-callout g-callout--warn&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;g-callout__body&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;g-callout__title&#34;&gt;Reporting&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If you experience or witness behaviour that makes you feel unsafe, tell any organizer at the event, or email &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;mailto:hello@example.com&#34;&gt;hello@example.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;. Reports are taken seriously and handled with discretion, and we will always protect the privacy of the person reporting.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
