    <item>
      <title>Get involved</title>
      <link>https://example.com/get-involved/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://example.com/get-involved/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;host-a-session&#34;&gt;Host a session&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;We&amp;rsquo;re always looking for members to lead a session! No experience necessary. Whether it&amp;rsquo;s your first time or your fiftieth, we welcome you, and we&amp;rsquo;ll help you prepare, rehearse, or even co-host.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Sessions run 20–30 minutes; show &amp;amp; tell spots are just five. Bring anything our community would love.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;a class=&#34;g-btn g-btn--primary&#34; href=&#34;mailto:hello@example.com?subject=Session%20idea&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-hand-sparkles&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;Suggest a session&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;offer-a-venue&#34;&gt;Offer a venue&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Have a room for 20–40 people, near transit, with step-free access? You can host our next gathering. Community halls, cafés and workplaces make wonderful hosts. See the &lt;a href=&#34;https://example.com/handbook/&#34;&gt;venue checklist&lt;/a&gt; for what we look for.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
